kquote>@神射手查馬克</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c758e10c4f152298b12a13372531ac3e0bb58e65","tid":288080,"uid":56403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"bba3f8f271a36d2f2deaff98930635d140ad2715","tid":288080,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔一排又出黎up廢話引人注意</blockquote><br />\n兇手嫌疑人之一：學友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你話初出道咁做都仲有人信<br />\n<br />\n91 年《每天愛你多一些》後已變一線歌王，有咁做既必要？"}]}